contents.markdown:
```WEBVTT

00:00.760 --> 00:02.560
<v Agent>Hi, thank you for calling Contoso Pharmacy.

00:02.560 --> 00:03.600
<v Agent>Who am I speaking with today?

00:04.720 --> 00:05.520
<v Customer>Good afternoon.

00:05.600 --> 00:06.320
<v Customer>My name is Mary.

00:06.360 --> 00:08.720
<v Customer>I'm calling about a refill for my prescribed medications.

00:08.720 --> 00:16.480
<v Customer>I have been trying to get a hold of someone for weeks and was told that I would get a call back regarding my situation, but it's been weeks and no one's contacted me, so I thought I'd call.

00:17.760 --> 00:19.280
<v Agent>I understand your frustration, Mary.

00:19.440 --> 00:21.520
<v Agent>Umm Can you tell me what exactly you're trying to accomplish?

00:22.640 --> 00:27.440
<v Customer>Yes, I'm trying to get a refill of my prescription drugs that my doctor prescribed to me for cholesterol.

00:29.120 --> 00:31.520
<v Agent>Okay, certainly happy to check that for you.

00:32.080 --> 00:32.880
<v Agent>One moment, please.

00:36.400 --> 00:40.000
<v Agent>I see here that you were on a generic form of Lipitor, is that right?

00:41.160 --> 00:43.360
<v Customer>Uh Yes, I was taking the generic form of Lipitor.

00:44.880 --> 00:50.400
<v Agent>Okay, so I see that your doctor stopped prescribing these drugs in 2021, actually.

00:51.800 --> 00:52.160
<v Customer>Oh, really?

00:52.160 --> 00:53.200
<v Customer>That doesn't sound right.

00:53.280 --> 00:55.080
<v Customer>I don't remember him canceling my prescription.

00:56.800 --> 01:02.720
<v Agent>OK, yeah, I'd be happy to check that for you because sometimes there's a gap in the system and it just doesn't get reported.

01:03.680 --> 01:05.280
<v Agent>So let me take a look here.

01:11.400 --> 01:12.600
<v Agent>Just a moment.

01:17.320 --> 01:23.800
<v Agent>So I'm seeing here that your doctor had these drugs prescribed to you from 2012 through 2021.

01:25.680 --> 01:26.400
<v Customer>Oh, huh.

01:26.400 --> 01:28.880
<v Customer>I mean, I'm definitely supposed to be taking something else.

01:29.360 --> 01:30.320
<v Customer>Would you check, please?

01:32.720 --> 01:32.960
<v Agent>Okay.

01:34.480 --> 01:40.080
<v Agent>Yeah, according to the latest records provided by the doctor's office, you're now on a different drug, metformin.

01:41.200 --> 01:45.640
<v Agent>Would you like us to go ahead and fill that prescription for you for pickup, the metformin 500 milligrams?

01:45.640 --> 01:45.680
<v Agent>Uh.

01:47.680 --> 01:49.040
<v Customer>Yeah, Yeah thank you so much.

01:49.120 --> 01:50.720
<v Customer>I'm almost out, so that'd be perfect.

01:52.080 --> 01:53.840
<v Agent>Uh You're very welcome, Mary.

01:54.000 --> 01:56.000
<v Agent>Please let us know if there's anything else we can do for you today.

01:57.120 --> 01:57.880
<v Customer>Okay, thank you.```

Summary.valueString: Mary called Contoso Pharmacy to inquire about a refill for her prescribed medications. She expressed frustration over not receiving a callback regarding her prescription. The agent checked her records and found that her doctor had stopped prescribing the generic form of Lipitor in 2021 and had switched her to metformin. The agent offered to fill the metformin prescription for pickup, which Mary accepted.
